        <updateDate>2012-02-21T17:04:25Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Earmark Elimination Act of 2011 - Makes it out of order in the House of Representatives to consider a bill, joint resolution, or any other measure that includes a congressional earmark or limited tax or tariff benefit.</p> <p>Makes a conforming amendment to Rule XXI (Restrictions on Certain Bills) of the Rules of the House of Representatives.]]></text>
      </summary>
